cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper deals with music genre classification, which is a subfield of music information retrieval (MIR). The use of neural networks for classification and the focus on both lyrics and audios suggest that the paper could belong to the following sub-categories: 

- cs.SD (Sound)
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.MM (Multimedia)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
